---
title: Easy Pork & Fennel Spaghetti Bolognese with Parmesan Cheese
description: Woohoo, spag bol night! There’s a reason this dish is so beloved in Australia – it’s bloody delicious. Tonight, we’re adding classic Italian pork and fennel for a very special touch.
